How to Compile and run
On Windows:
1.Open command Prompt
2.Compile with: g++ car_racing.cpp -o car_racing
3.Run with: car_racing

On Linux/Mac:
1.Open Terminal
2.Compile with: g++ car_racing.cpp -o car_racing -lncurses
3.Run with: ./car_racing

Game Features:
1.Menu System: Start game, view instructions, or quit

2.Scoreboard: Shows current score, high score, and speed

3.Controls: A (left), D (right), Q (quit)

4.Progressive Difficulty: Game speeds up as you score more points

5.Collision Detection: Hitting obstacles ends the game

6.Cross-Platform: Works on Windows, Linux, and macOS

